headline: The TJX Companies, Inc. Announces Quarterly Common Stock Dividend
summary: FRAMINGHAM, Mass., December 09, 2025--The TJX Companies, Inc. (NYSE: TJX) today announced the declaration of a quarterly dividend on its common stock of $.425 per share payable March 5, 2026, to shareholders of record on February 12, 2026.
